review_blob: Aromas of grapefruit and tangerine lead into an abundance of fresh pine and tropical fruit notes followed by a crisp, resinous bitterness. The complex hop profile is supported by a firm malt presence to create an incredibly flavorful and well-balanced IPA
Growler.  No head, hazy body, light hop to moderate aroma.  Nice rye flavor.
beer_name: Wisconsin Dells Rye India Pale Ale
